295
00:27:09,220 --> 00:27:10,200
[SPEAKER_00] Kome se želiš svidjet?

296
00:27:12,480 --> 00:27:18,599
[SPEAKER_02] Znaš šta, dobro pitanje, prije svega sebi.

297
00:27:18,599 --> 00:27:27,180
